lead_paragraph: Michael Phelps will swim in likely his final race in an American pool while Katie Ledecky is expected to chase a world record as the two biggest attractions at the U.S. Olympic trials take their final bows on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Phelps Ready to Take Final Bow at U.S. Trials
